sections.text: reports; how treated.All reports of child abuse or neglect which are not under subdivision (1)(a), (b), or (c) of section 28-720 shall be considered unfounded and shall be maintained only in the tracking system of child protection cases pursuant to section 28-715 and not in the central registry of child protection cases maintained pursuant to section 28-718.SourceLaws 2005, LB 116, ยง 12;Laws 2014, LB853, ยง 10;Laws 2015, LB292, ยง 3.
